InsufficientFundsException Class:
/**
 * InsufficientFundsException class is a custom exception used
 * when there are insufficient funds in the account for a withdrawal.
 */
public class InsufficientFundsException extends Exception {
    public InsufficientFundsException(String message) {
        super(message);
    }
}

Enhanced WithdrawalTransaction (with Exception Handling):
@Override
public void apply(BankAccount ba) {
    try {
        if (ba.getBalance() < amount) {
            throw new InsufficientFundsException("Insufficient balance for withdrawal.");
        }
        ba.withdraw(amount); // Withdraw the specified amount
    } catch (InsufficientFundsException e) {
        System.out.println(e.getMessage()); // Handle insufficient funds exception
    } finally {
        System.out.println("Transaction attempted.");
    }
}

